🤖 MechDesignCopilot is the first AI skill specifically designed for mechanical engineering. It
  provides comprehensive guidance from conceptual design to manufacturing documentation, covering
  structural design, parametric calculations, 3D modeling, BOM generation, and mechatronics
  integration.

  ✨ Features:
  - Full-process guidance (Requirements → Design → BOM)
  - Confirmation-driven interaction (design partner, not generator)
  - Layered output for all skill levels
  - Mechatronics integration (mechanical + electrical)
  - Complete templates and examples
